/blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁咪係囉，香港地方咁細，根本就唔應該拎外國個d大城市個個都可以渣車黎比。<br />\n<br />\n唔講支那講台北啦，2010年，台北個捷運係咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/05W4eKj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F05W4eKj.png&h=63d1c3ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日已經變成咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AGH77g8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAGH77g8.jpg&h=9acd97d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n反觀 2010 香港個地鐵係咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oQ1g6r5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoQ1g6r5.jpg&h=db1ddc16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家，先多得個少少野<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKYJSY9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKYJSY9.jpg&h=7f5c0548&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"24884770d04d9c0dff7ff98c0317d7cafb2c4162","tid":180593,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T05:57:55.000Z","msg":"上面d圖亂曬嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔講支那講台北啦，2010年，台北個捷運係咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/05W4eKj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F05W4eKj.png&h=63d1c3ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日已經變成咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKYJSY9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKYJSY9.jpg&h=7f5c0548&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反觀 2010 香港個地鐵係咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AGH77g8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAGH77g8.jpg&h=9acd97d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家，先多得個少少野<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oQ1g6r5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoQ1g6r5.jpg&h=db1ddc16&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"286e7335e7c3331c6f89541e664c2c6524400850","tid":180593,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T06:3